dct_title_s: [Holy Land map of Nile River Delta and surrounding areas]
dct_description_sm: Decorative cartouches containing descriptive text; "RND" above cartouche on right.
Depicts partial route of Israelites in desert; shows buildings, topography, vegetation, ship, sea monster.
From Münster's Cosmographia universalis, 1544-1628 (published by Henri Petri 1544-1550), French edition (published in 1552, 1556, 1560, 1565, 1568, 1575).
